Adoption Analytics App Considerations
Datasets created for the app count against row limits for your CRM Analytics license.
Only CRM Analytics logs are included. To include Salesforce logs, use Event Monitoring.
The first time you use Adoption Analytics, it can take 24 hours for data to be collected in the event logs and logs data to register in the app’s datasets and dashboard.
Salesforce stores event log data for 30 days.
CRM Analytics stores event log data in a dataset for up to 365 days, which counts against your license’s row limit.
